					<h1 class="display-6 mt-5">Extras 🔧</h1>
					<p>1 - Para crear un usuario para backups:</p>
					<pre class=""><code class="language-sql">CREATE USER 'backup'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'passwd';</code></pre>
